"title": "5362: justice, in believers' lives",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5362",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God requires justice to be evident in the lives of his people. Through justification, believers are granted the status of being righteous in his sight, and are called upon to live out that righteousness in their lives.</p>\n<h2>God's law demands justice</h2>\n<h3>The law is written on the conscience</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:14-Rom2:15\">ROM 2:14–2:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen20:5-Gen20:6\">GEN 20:5–20:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:27\">PRO 20:27</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:7\">ISA 51:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl8:5\">ECC 8:5</a></p>\n<h3>The law in the OT</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:1-Exod20:3\">EXO 20:1–20:3</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:4-Deut6:5\">DEU 6:4–6:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:4-Exod20:17\">EXO 20:4–20:17</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:6-Deut5:21\">DEU 5:6–5:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:1\">PSA 119:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:165\">PSA 119:165</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:37-Matt22:40\">MAT 22:37–22:40</a></p>\n<h3>The law in the NT</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:17\">MAT 5:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:7\">ROM 7:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:12\">ROM 7:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:22\">ROM 7:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:10\">ROM 13:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:8-1Tim1:11\">1TI 1:8–1:11</a></p>\n<h2>Justification is by faith</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:17\">ROM 1:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:4\">HAB 2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen15:6\">GEN 15:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:21-Rom3:24\">ROM 3:21–3:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom4:24-Rom4:25\">ROM 4:24–4:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:1\">ROM 5:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:30\">ROM 9:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:6\">GAL 3:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:24\">GAL 3:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:9\">PHP 3:9</a></p>\n<h2>The marks of the just person</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:17\">JAS 2:17</a></strong> <em>Although justification is by faith alone it is always to be accompanied by righteous behaviour.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:34-Matt25:36\">MAT 25:34–25:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:10\">EPH 2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:7\">1JN 3:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:9\">1JN 3:9</a></p>\n<h3>Thinking justly</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps1:2\">PSA 1:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps24:4\">PSA 24:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:8\">PSA 40:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:111-Ps119:112\">PSA 119:111–119:112</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:8\">MAT 5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:8\">PHP 4:8</a></p>\n<h3>Speaking justly</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps141:3\">PSA 141:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov4:24\">PRO 4:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:6-Prov8:8\">PRO 8:6–8:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:25\">EPH 4:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:10\">1PE 3:10</a></p>\n<h3>Behaving justly</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:8\">MIC 6:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:25\">DEU 6:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:3\">PSA 106:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:3\">PRO 21:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:15-Isa33:16\">ISA 33:15–33:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts24:16\">ACT 24:16</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of just people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:8\">JOB 1:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam8:15\">2SA 8:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:11-1Kgs3:12\">1KI 3:11–3:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:28\">1KI 3:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:50-Luke23:51\">LUK 23:50–23:51</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts25:8\">ACT 25:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts25:11\">ACT 25:11</a></p>\n<h2>The vindication of the just</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:8\">2TI 4:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps86:17\">PSA 86:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan12:3\">DAN 12:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:9-Rev7:17\">REV 7:9–7:17</a></p>",
